Maintainer: Monah Abou Alezz <monah.aboualezz@igm.cnr.it>
Description: Analysis of gene annotations data using the GENCODE database <https://www.gencodegenes.org/> for the human and mouse genomes can be performed through the functions implemented in this package.
    The user is able to analyse and extract different types of data based on the annotations published in the different verions of GENCODE database and the comparison of data from these releases.
